## Warning — Flag but Don't Block

These are flagged inline. Must be resolved before `speckit-checklist` passes.

| Pattern | Warning |
|---------|---------|
| Missing `[Authorize]` on new controller / endpoint | Add or explicitly document as public with a comment |
| PII (emails, phone numbers) logged at INFO level | Downgrade to DEBUG or mask before logging |
| Missing `SameSite` cookie attribute | Set `SameSite=Strict` or `Lax`; document if `None` is required |
| Auth endpoints without rate limiting | Add middleware or attribute-based rate limiting |
| No input length validation | DoS risk; add `MaxLength` / FluentValidation `MaximumLength` |
| `appsettings.json` with non-placeholder values | Move to environment-specific gitignored file or Key Vault |

